" to get the output of a command in a new tab, just enter :TabEx <cmd>
function! TabEx(cmd)
  redir => message
  silent execute a:cmd
  redir END
  tabnew
  silent put=message
  set nomodified
endfunction
command! -nargs=+ -complete=command TabEx call TabEx(<q-args>)
